==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Silkiness
<hw>Silk"i*ness</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The
quality or state of being silky or silken; softness and
smoothness.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Fig.: Effeminacy; weakness.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>
<rj><au>B. Jonson.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Silkman</ent>⟦br⟧
